ValueSet    : CID_3757
Id          : dicom-cid-3757-CardiacDiagnosticProcedure
Description :
"""
In a prior version of this Context Group, the code P5-B3009 was specified for Exercise stress echocardiography. That code has been retired by SNOMED, and replaced by P5-B3050. Although there is minimal possibility of misinterpretation with SOP Instances that may include the retired code, receiving applications should be aware of this change; seechapter_J

The content in this ValueSet is based on [CID 3757](https://dicom.nema.org/medical/dicom/current/output/chtml/part16/sect_CID_3757.html).
"""
